snippet.title: Mechanized Corps: Rebirth Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Mechanized Corps: Rebirth will be available in early access on Steam on March 11th.  Wishlist is now at https://store.steampowered.com/app/3434530/Mechanized_Corps_Rebirth/

Join us on Discord as well at  https://discord.gg/VM9bdrtNyU
